"अस्तिनिम्नलिखित कीलदबावानां सर्वेषां"

#: kaccess/kaccess.notifyrc:582
msgctxt "Name"
msgid "A lock key has been activated"
msgstr "एकः तालाकुंजी सक्रियः अभवत्"

#: kaccess/kaccess.notifyrc:663
msgctxt "Comment"
msgid ""
"A lock key (e.g. Caps Lock or Num Lock) has changed its state and is now "
"active"
msgstr ""
"एकः तालाकुंजी (उदा. Caps Lock अथवा Num Lock) स्वस्य स्थितिं परिवर्तयति अधुना च "
"अस्तिसक्रियं"

#: kaccess/kaccess.notifyrc:743
msgctxt "Name"
msgid "A lock key has been deactivated"
msgstr "एकः तालाकुंजी निष्क्रियः अभवत्"

#: kaccess/kaccess.notifyrc:824
msgctxt "Comment"
msgid ""
"A lock key (e.g. Caps Lock or Num Lock) has changed its state and is now "
